::Prowl/Reptilica::

Prowl's eyes widen as Iron Raptor pushes Reptilica's weapon down, the 
Alliance bot growling.

"Allright," Reptilica says to Iron Raptor, turning back around, "If that 
Maximal doesn't listen, your friend here can blow this base sky high."
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Prowl raises an eyebrow at Iron Raptor's expression. He was surprised that 
she had just done that, with the autoguns and rifles aimed at her.

Prowl starts walking as Reptilica does, staying 10 feet behind the other.
